posting_body: ['San Francisco - Balboa Park - Home for rent', '2900sf 4bed/3.5 Bath Outer Mission Home', 'Link to mobile layout: \xa0 <URL>', 'Summary:', 'Rent: $6250', 'Bed / Bath: 4 / 3.5', 'Type: Home', 'Term: 12 Months', 'Please contact:', 'Chuck Totah \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Description:', 'Spacious and bright 2938sf 3-Level 4bed/3.5baths Contemporary single-family home in Balboa Park/Outer Mission Gated Community.', '\xa0 Newer, 1997, construction.', '\xa0 Main level includes large living room with high ceiling and fireplace, separate formal dining room, gourmet kitchen with eat-in breakfast area, stainless appliances, laundry closet w/ washer & dryer and half bath.', 'Top level features 3BD/2BA,\xa0 en-suite primary bedroom with two wall to wall closets.', 'Lower level features a 1 bedroom 1 full bath and a family room, 2 car garage and low maintenance back patio.', 'Centrally located near Mission, Alemany & Geneva Streets.', '\xa0 Walk to BART, Muni, and local shops and restaurants.', 'Easy freeway access.', '~\xa0 Pets considered (restriction apply)', '~ Tenant pays all utilities\\', '~ Excellent credit / $40 app fee per adult', 'Details:', 'Floors: Hardwood & Carpet', 'Kitchen: Upgraded', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Outside area: Patio', 'Parking: 2 Car Garage', 'Parking Fee: $0', 'Pets:   Cat,    Dog    OK', 'View: Neighborhood', 'Location:', 'Chancery Lane & Alemany Blvd, San Francisco, California', 'Meet the J.Wavro Team:', '<URL>', 'Please contact:', 'Chuck Totah \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Preview more properties at <URL>', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'Content and Images © 2003 - 2021 J.Wavro \xa0 | \xa0 BRE # 01810008 \xa0 | \xa0 cl31386992014789-0']
